Karl Ernst von Baer

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Karl Ernst von Baer





Born
(1792-02-17)17 February 1792
Piep estate, Governorate of Livonia, Russian Empire


Died
16 November 1876(1876-11-16) (aged 84)
Dorpat, Russian Empire


Citizenship
Russian Empire


Nationality
German


Fields
Biology, embryology, geology, meteorology, geography


