Grand Touring (GT) & Grand Touring Plus (GT+)




The Baer "GT" brake system is designed primarily for late-model Mustangs and the Subaru WRX (excluding the STi).
he large 2-Piston PBR pin-driven calipers provide increased pad volume for a measurable increase in performance.
Rotors are 1-Pc and come in 12.75" to 13" diameters, depending on the application.
Cross-drilled, slotted and zinc-coated surfaces
The Baer "GT-PLUS" covers a wide range of larger, heavier cars, trucks and SUVs and is a cost-effective 6-Piston EXTREME-PLUS





