EradiSpeed+ Front and Rear




EradiSpeed+ are stock size direct replacement rotors that are a 2-pc design
Designed to be used with factory calipers EradiSpeed™ rotors feature premium high silicon content iron castings.
Rotor plates or outer rotor surfaces are cast with additional mass to absorb additional heat.
Internal curved and directional vanes maximize air flow and cooling.
Externally slotting and drilling alleviate friction losses from pad outgassing and a zinc chromate



